Label: assess_msg_publish_content
English: Are you sure you want to publish this learning outcome?
Chinese: 确定要发布这个学习成果吗？

Label: assess_msg_delete_content
English: Are you sure you want to delete this learning outcome?
Chinese: 确定要删除这个学习成果吗？

Label: assess_msg_remove_select_one
English: At least one learning outcome should be selected.
Chinese: 至少选择一个学习成果。

Label: assess_msg_republish_content
English: Are you sure you want to republish this learning outcome?

Label: assess_msg_reject_reason
English: Please specify the reason for rejection.
